OL,6,FGroups of mourners gathered in Lytham
OL,7,Fto farewell the little boy
OL,9,FA toddler from Blackpool, who was
OL,10,Fmurdered by his own father, has been
OL,11,Flaid to rest.
OL,13,FDamion Russell, who was just two years
OL,14,Fold, was viciously assaulted by his
OL,15,Ffather Daniel Hardcastle, 31, in
OL,16,FAugust 2023. It happened within weeks
OL,17,Fof Hardcastle being granted full-time
OL,18,Fcare of the little boy.
