OL,6,FDamion was brought to St Cuthbert's
OL,7,FChurch in Lytham, Lancashire in a
OL,8,Fhorse-drawn carriage.
OL,10,FMourners at the service were asked to
OL,11,Fwear blue and an open invitation was
OL,12,Fextended to the entire community to
OL,13,Fensure as many people as possible
OL,14,Fcommemorated Damion's short life.
OL,16,FDamion died after suffering a
OL,17,Ftraumatic head injury with his father,
OL,18,FHardcastle, claiming the toddler had
OL,19,Finjured himself after falling and
OL,20,Fhitting his head on a coffee table.
